==English==

===Pronunciation===
*:Rhymes: [[Rhymes:English:-uːdən|-uːdən]]

===Noun===
'''Bermudan'''

#A person from [[Bermuda]] or of Bermudian descent.
see: [[Bermudian]]

===Adjective===
'''Bermudan'''

#Of, from, or pertaining to Bermuda, or the Bermudian people.
see: [[Bermudian]]

Usage note: No inhabitant of Bermuda ever uses the word 'Bermudan' to describe themselves. The term 'Bermudian' is always used instead. As such, use of 'Bermudan' should be considered incorrect.